This is a simple web application having a Web form and flask app as the backend using postgres sql as database.

Folder Details : 

k8s -- Contains manifests and helm charts.
src -- Contains Application code.
Terraform -- Contains Terraform configuration files.

Steps to Run the flask Application 

1. Apply the Terraform configuration file to create a necessary resources for EKS cluster which
is using s3 as a backend . 
2. Deploy helm charts and Manifests to the eks cluster.
3. Access the application using load balancer end point on port 8000.
